JAVA Code execution

Open powershell from the project folder

mvn clean

mvn package

java -cp .\target\spark_project-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT-jar-with-dependencies.jar com.spark.helper.Driver

Docker execution

Command 1: 

docker build -t writetextfileimage .

Command 2:

docker run -v C:/Users/Anurag/Desktop/docker-service/:/root/docker-service writetextfileimage

docker run -v C:/Users/Anurag/Desktop/spark_project/:/root/spark_project sparkprojectimages

docker login --username=pkankariya --email=pkkdg@mail.umkc.edu

Tag image created

	docker tag 2286fec48b7d pkankariya/poonamk:firsttry

Push to repository

	docker push pkankariya/poonamk
	
Pull from repository

	docker pull pkankariya/poonamk:firsttry

Run the project on Docker

docker run -v C:/Users/Anurag/Desktop/PB_Final_Results/:/root/spark-project pkankariya/poonamk:firsttry 

